fields.text: Have made it through the whole week doing my 10,000 steps a day!
The book "Easy Vegan" really helped me stick with meal prepping this week. Highly recommend.
The podcast 'Stop smoking' has been keeping me on track. 2 weeks no smoking! Try it out.
Trello has been a great tool to help organise my work projects. If anyone needs a hand with getting to grips with it, happy to help :)
I feel so different meditating every day! My 10mins is perfect. On to week 4...
Lizzie, the grid instructor, is great at motivating us with different exercises. Try out her classes!
The Headspace app is highly recommended, it's working for me
The 10mins TED talks every day have been a good source of motivation. Give them a go :)
